  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Be an ambassador of mtm labo.</li>\n  <li>Access clients' needs and provide professional advice.</li>\n  <li>Perform treatment services according to standards set by the company.</li>\n  <li>Recommend, educate and promote suitable treatments and products to clients.</li>\n  <li>Ensure client's satisfaction and comfort after each treatment therapy.</li>\n  <li>Build and establish good rapport with customers.</li>\n  <li>Assist in retail operations. eg. stock take.</li>\n  <li>Maintain general housekeeping duties and maintenance of the cleanliness of the work stations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Cidesco, ITE, CIBTAC and other beauty related qualifications.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of skin concept and hands-on facial  massage techniques.</li>\n  <li>Positive and willing to learn attitude.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and Interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Service Oriented and customer focused.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Preferably Junior Executive specialized in Personal Care/Beauty/Fitness Service or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and good team player.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
